{"tid":290636,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民族黨6.30集會「悼淪陷20年」","createTime":"2017-06-20T02:25:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-28T01:20:30.000Z","uid":25558,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"72234b131a6d72e255fb217915a7d455bb76f88c","tid":290636,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T02:25:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20062086&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170620\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20062086%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170620&d=YgJuT%2F1eacVT0fIfCeo4oQIBMskQiLF9ooRt%2FFIrCZo%3D&h=18bbfc32\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20062086%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170620&h=970567a8\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20062086&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170620</a><br />\n<br />\n民族黨6.30集會「悼淪陷20年」<br />\n<br />\n要聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n陳浩天指香港民族黨不會參與民陣的7.1大遊行。王子俊攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】久未露面的香港民族黨召集人陳浩天昨召開記者會宣佈，將於本月30日、7.1回歸前夕在尖沙嘴鐘樓舉行歷時兩至三小時的聚會，表達港人有感回歸20年猶如淪陷的聲音，預計聚會有300人出席，屆時有音樂、影片、悼念和嘉賓分享。他明言香港民族黨不會參與人間民權陣線舉辦的7.1大遊行，形容該黨較民陣更敢言，明言：「我哋會講中共政權滾出香港，佢哋唔會。」<br />\n<br />\n陳浩天稱盼團結獨派<br />\n<br />\n陳浩天昨日在中環和平紀念碑會見傳媒，其間多名便衣和軍裝警員在場監視，並全程錄影。陳指民族黨將於下周五、即6月30日在尖沙嘴鐘樓旁舉行晚會，透過和平、理性方式讓市民表達不滿中央政府和特區政府管治的聲音，緬懷回歸前的光輝歲月，「畀香港人諗番起我哋曾經幾咁風光、幾咁巴閉」。<br />\n他指，晚會希望團結港獨、本土派的市民，指獨派已重整旗鼓，並說：「如果我哋唔企出嚟發表意見，全世界都會覺得，原來香港人係非常歡迎中國統治。」<br />\n他昨上午已向警方申請不反對通知書，但警方初步反應不太正面，形容該黨的集會風險高，他表明該黨集會和平理性，盼警方批出不反對通知書，避免不愉快事情發生；若警方反對申請，民族黨或會舉辦示威等其他活動，甚至透過參與慶回歸活動表達不同聲音，但暫未有具體應變計劃。<br />\n■記者姚國雄<br />\n<br />\n97年主權移交至今，香港前進還是倒退？「蘋果」與你細數廿載風雨。<br />\n【回歸二十年】專頁：&nbsp;<a href=\"http://hksar20.appledaily.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhksar20.appledaily.com.hk&d=YgJuT%2F1eacVT0fIfCeo4oQIBMskQiLF9ooRt%2FFIrCZo%3D&h=1069113f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hksar20.appledaily.com.hk</a>￼"},{"pid":"870fd4edb5eb74a4362da87a5fc40ce3b3bbedcb","tid":290636,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T02:26:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170620/large/20la2p06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170620%2Flarge%2F20la2p06.jpg&h=6d4b3c15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳浩天指香港民族黨不會參與民陣的7.1大遊行。王子俊攝"},{"pid":"bfa6a7ae4a9730f81df0e3fdc3d824b105aa9d64","tid":290636,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T02:26:45.000Z","msg":"我會參加 7.1 大遊行"},{"pid":"b412ed9fea77ef2a6f584517e0176fa2ae623060","tid":290636,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T02:34:50.000Z","msg":"做咩學埋飯民D野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e8c77124f5330101c6a7fa055825ac88018472f","tid":290636,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T03:53:29.000Z","msg":"123"},{"pid":"51274bf5accc411f4fd1aeec48cefa44fe75431c","tid":290636,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T03:57:22.000Z","msg":"123"},{"pid":"863cb34702b0f30b45c22eb3e062519d79c203b9","tid":290636,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T10:51:21.000Z","msg":"132"},{"pid":"ff41eb55ef6fb3ec9699c76017b520a2d4178645","tid":290636,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T02:23:48.000Z","msg":"123"},{"pid":"ca76734fc199a8d136bb4148c65689fc5d5921b8","tid":290636,"uid":49784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T03:45:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f1c931159cc2e3a28115564e